Package org.dellroad.muxable

A Java library for multiplexing multiple byte-oriented channels over a single parent channel.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MuxableChannel
    A single channel supporting parallel nested byte-oriented channels operating independently.
    NestedChannelRequest
    Represents nested channel(s) newly created by the remote side.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Directions
    Used to specifify which of input and/or output directions are desired.
